      <img src="pics/shibcrossing.jpg"/>
      <h1> Shibuya Crossing </h1>
      <p> This famous crosswalk is in the district of Shibuya. Shibuya has great
        shops, restaurants, and entertainment while constantly being surrounded
        by tall buildings and people. </p>
    </section>
    <section>
      <img src="pics/tokyopark.jpg"/>
      <h1> Parks and Gardens </h1>
      <p> Though it might make you think you are in a different city, Tokyo has many
      parks and gardens scattered throughout the city.  </p>
    </section>
    <section>
      <img src="pics/iliketrains.jpg"/>
      <h1> Tokyo Trains </h1>
      <p> Tokyo has one of the best public transportation systems in the world.
      if you get the chance to take a bullet train outside the city, it's highly
      recommended.</p>
    </section>
